                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$e - Status</strong> <div class="description">Text that explains or clarifies the status of the patent document identified by
                              the number in the field.
         </div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">Status usually relates to the examination of an application or the
                                 granting/publishing of a patent.
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="example">
            <table width="100%">
               <tr>
                  <td valign="top" width="5%" align="left"></td>
