                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>93-10077<strong>$b</strong>xxu<strong>$c</strong>patent<strong>$d</strong>19930322<strong>$e</strong>continuation
                  </td>
               </tr>
               <tr>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="1" align="left"><strong>013</strong></td>
                  <td vAlign="top" colspan="9" align="left"><strong>##</strong><strong>$a</strong>74-2202467<strong>$b</strong>xxu<strong>$c</strong>patent<strong>$d</strong>19740305<strong>$e</strong>published
                  </td>
               </tr>
            </table>
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$f - Party to document</strong> <div class="description">Information that identifies the country or agency that is party to the document,
                              usually an application for patent or related document. Codes from: <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/countries/">MARC Code List for Countries</a></em> and <em><a href="http://www.loc.gov/marc/organizations/orgshome.html">MARC Code List
                                          for Organizations</a></em>. 
         </div>
         <div class="description2">
            <div class="description">May contain a code identifying, when appropriate, an organization (generally an
                                 international one).
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="example">
